OL,4,CRetail bosses demand more protection
OL,5,Cfor UK workers
OL,6, Retail leaders are urging the UK
OL,7, government to follow Scotland's example
OL,8, in extending new protections for shop
OL,9, workers.
OL,11,FThe Protection of Workers Act comes
OL,12,Finto force in Scotland on Tuesday,
OL,13,Fwhich makes assaulting or abusing
OL,14,Fretail staff a standalone offence.
OL,16,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC) and
OL,17,Funion Usdaw want similar rules to be
OL,18,Fintroduced across the rest of the UK.
OL,20,FBRC boss Helen Dickinson said "enough
OL,21,Fis enough".
